-: Steps to Use the code :-

>> Make sure the declared port number is available (not being utilised by other programs) on your system, and if it is 
not available then try changing the port number int both client side and server side of code.

>> Then Run the "Server.java" file, this will activate the server.
>> Then run the "Client.java" file, this will activate a client.

This code shows us the Two way Communication using socket programming which takes input from the client and gives predefined replies from the server sde of the code.
